      "full_name": "Design Bureau “Mikrob”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Design Bureau Mikrob is a Russian entity which produces first-person view (FPV) unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) for the Russian army. In 2024, the company announced plans to deliver 3 000 UAVs equipped with AI autopilot to the frontline in Ukraine. In August 2024, the Microb-10 UAV was successfully deployed by operators from the 35th Motorised Rifle Guards Aleyskaya Brigade of the 41st Army against a Ukrainian tank. Citizens of Novosibirsk, part of the All-Russia People’s Front organisation, successfully sent 40 combat FPV UAVs to the Russian troops involved in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}